Invocation Name: five minute recipes
des: You're fed up with eating ready-cooked meals but don't know how to cook? You want to impress your friends but don't have hours to spend in the kitchen? Five-Minute recipes is here to help you find easy and tasty recipes for breakfast, lunch, snack or dinner. In less than 5 minutes, Five-Minute recipes will help you step by step make a delicious meal!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
